<body>
<div id="country3" class="tabcontent">
<div style="width: 740px; border: 1px dashed gray; padding: 10px;  margin:0px auto;">
<h2>IPD Clinical Chart</h2>
<hr />
<span class="title">Screen Overview </span><br />
This screen captures the details of all patient IPD clinical chart entry details based on user login ward.
<br /><hr /><br />
<img src="images/IPD_clinicalchart.jpg" width="725"  /><br /><br />
<hr />

<p>

<span class="title">Load:</span><br />
Based on login ward all admitted patient list will display.
<br />
<span class="title">Date:</span> <br />
It is system date, user can’t modify this date. 
<br />
  <span class="title">Time:</span> 
    <br />It is system time, user can modify this time. 
<br />
    <span class="title">Go:</span> 
    <br />If user press go button same time will copy for all patients.
<br />
    <span class="title">Ad No:</span> 
    <br />This is patient admission number, user can’t modify this number. it will come based on admission.
<br />
    <span class="title">Patient Name:</span> 
    <br />Based on admission number patient name will appear, user can’t modify this number.
<br />
    <span class="title">Time:</span> 
    <br />It is system time, based on above time this time will change, user can modify this time.
    
    <br />
    <span class="title">Temperature:</span> 
    <br />User can select the temperature from the given list, this will come from free defined list and it can remain blank.
    
    <br />
    <span class="title">Pulse:</span> 
    <br />User can write present patient pulse details, it can remain blank.
    
    <br />
    <span class="title">Respiration:</span> 
    <br />User can write present patient respiration details, it can remain blank.
    
    <br />
    <span class="title">BP:</span> 
    <br />User can write present patient BP details, it can remain blank.
    
    <br />
    <span class="title">Bowel:</span> 
    <br />User can write present patient bowel details, it can remain blank.
    
    <br />
    <span class="title">Pain:</span> 
    <br />User can select the pain from the given list, this will come from free defined list and it can remain blank.
    
    <br />
    <span class="title">FHR:</span> 
    <br />User can write present patient FHR details, it can remain blank.

    <br />
    <span class="title">Remarks:</span> 
    <br />User can write present patient remarks or observations, it can remain blank.
    
    <br />
    <span class="title">Submit (Button):</span> 
    <br />By clicking on Submit button user can save the data. 
    
    <br />
    <span class="title">Print (Button):</span> 
    <br />By clicking on any patient user can take patient clinical chart print out. 
    
    <br />
    <span class="title">View (Button):</span> 
    <br />By clicking on any patient user can view the patient previous history details.
    
    <br />
    <span class="title">Back (Button):</span> 
    <br />Clicking on Back button, will move user to the previous screen. 

    
        
</p>


</div>
